%% Models as a Service - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as maas-default-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS Terminate
    participant AuthPolicy as Kuadrant AuthPolicy<br/>TokenReview + SAR
    participant RateLimit as Kuadrant RateLimitPolicy<br/>Tier-based Limits
    participant MaaSAPI as maas-api<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KServe as LLMInferenceService<br/>Backend 8000/TCP

    Note over Client,KServe: Flow 1: Model Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA token)
    Gateway->>AuthPolicy: Validate Token<br/>KubernetesTokenReview
    AuthPolicy->>MaaSAPI: POST /v1/tiers/lookup<br/>(tier enrichment callback)
    MaaSAPI-->>AuthPolicy: Tier: premium
    AuthPolicy->>AuthPolicy: SubjectAccessReview<br/>post llminferenceservices
    AuthPolicy-->>Gateway: Auth OK + tier metadata
    Gateway->>RateLimit: Check rate limit<br/>(user: jane, tier: premium, 20/2m)
    RateLimit-->>Gateway: Allowed
    Gateway->>KServe: Proxy inference request<br/>HTTPS/8000
    KServe-->>Gateway: Inference response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,K8sAPI: Flow 2: Token Issuance
    Client->>Gateway: POST /maas-api/v1/tokens<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>AuthPolicy: KubernetesTokenReview
    AuthPolicy-->>Gateway: Auth OK
    Gateway->>MaaSAPI: Forward request<br/>X-MaaS-Username / X-MaaS-Group headers
    MaaSAPI->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceAccount<br/>(in {instance}-tier-{tier} namespace)
    K8sAPI-->>MaaSAPI: SA created
    MaaSAPI->>K8sAPI: TokenRequest API<br/>(audience: maas-default-gateway-sa,<br/>expiration: 4h default)
    K8sAPI-->>MaaSAPI: JWT token
    MaaSAPI-->>Gateway: Token response
    Gateway-->>Client: {"token": "eyJ..."}

    Note over Client,MaaSAPI: Flow 3: Model Listing
    Client->>Gateway: GET /v1/models<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>AuthPolicy: KubernetesTokenReview
    AuthPolicy-->>Gateway: Auth OK
    Gateway->>MaaSAPI: Forward request<br/>X-MaaS-Username / X-MaaS-Group headers
    MaaSAPI->>MaaSAPI: Read from informer cache<br/>(LLMInferenceService + InferenceService)
    MaaSAPI-->>Gateway: OpenAI-compatible model list
    Gateway-->>Client: {"data": [{"id": "model-1", ...}]}
